    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Head, thorax, and abdomen of dorsal and lateral views in males: A, B. Phortica (Phortica) cardua (Okada, 1977); C, D. P. (P.) eugamma (Toda & Peng, 1990); E, F. P. (P.) gamma (Toda & Peng, 1990); G, H. P. (P.) glabtabula Chen & Gao, 2005; I, J. P. (P.) okadai (Máca, 1977). Scale bars = 1 mm." ;
